{"tid":767138,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[大把機會] ﻿今年請六千七百新公僕 紀律部隊佔近半","createTime":"2018-08-04T08:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T12:19:06.000Z","uid":116083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fc468a82ec62cd1cdbaa502f20ee21a31a0beb94","tid":767138,"uid":116083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:35:52.000Z","msg":"　　為應對公僕退休潮，特區政府今年度將增聘六千七百個職位，除了入職門檻較低的約一千個助理文書主任，有約三千個紀律部隊職位，申請難度較高，但薪酬亦高，料成為應屆大學畢業生必爭的筍工。<br />\n<br />\n　　政府大增公務員人手，在本財政年度加多六千七百個職位，政務司司長張建宗曾解釋政府今年需要大增六千七百名公務員的原因，他指隨着第二次世界大戰後「嬰兒潮」人士踏入退休年齡，公務員退休高峰期亦來臨，因退休帶來的公務員自然流失率，到二一至二二年度五年間將升至約百分之四，所以政府會積極招募新血。<br />\n<br />\n　　<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在各紀律部隊中，警方將招聘一千零五十七人，人數最多。隨着港珠澳大橋、高鐵香港段及蓮塘香園圍口岸三大基建項目陸續落成，入境處將請八百二十四人，而海關會聘請七百六十六人。消防處亦招聘三百八十三人。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人工 &amp; 晉升階梯</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nPolice Inspector 督察<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/police-inspector-superintendent/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fpolice-inspector-superintendent%2F&d=FNLUDaUGLpi5VR9P9Y2fJbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=fee7a9be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/police-inspector-superintendent/</a><br />\n<br />\nPolice Constable 警員<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/police-constable/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fpolice-constable%2F&d=FNLUDaUGLpi5VR9P9Y2fJbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=9ed990e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/police-constable/</a><br />\n<br />\nImmigration Officer 入境事務主任<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/immigration-officer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fimmigration-officer%2F&d=FNLUDaUGLpi5VR9P9Y2fJbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=4530f518\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/immigration-officer/</a><br />\n<br />\nImmigration Assistant 入境事務助理員<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/immigration-assistant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fimmigration-assistant%2F&d=FNLUDaUGLpi5VR9P9Y2fJbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=2e1ee7ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/immigration-assistant/</a><br />\n<br />\nInspector of Customs and Excise 海關督察<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/inspector-superintendent-of-customs-and-excise/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Finspector-superintendent-of-customs-and-excise%2F&d=FNLUDaUGLpi5VR9P9Y2fJbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=3e0547c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/inspector-superintendent-of-customs-and-excise/</a><br />\n<br />\nCustoms Officer 關員<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/customs-officer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fcustoms-officer%2F&d=FNLUDaUGLpi5VR9P9Y2fJbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=b55998da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/customs-officer/</a><br />\n<br />\nStation Officer 消防隊長<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/station-officer-divisional-officer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fstation-officer-divisional-officer%2F&d=FNLUDaUGLpi5VR9P9Y2fJbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=6d13c501\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/station-officer-divisional-officer/</a><br />\n<br />\nFireman 消防員<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/fireman/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Ffireman%2F&d=FNLUDaUGLpi5VR9P9Y2fJbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=8a6773f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/fireman/</a><br />\n<br />\n　　其他新職位較多的部門，包括地政總署請三百七十八人、社會福利署請二百九十二人，而康文署請二百四十二人。"},{"pid":"cba1c17912f781ae41f444c2814e2c39f54b20e2","tid":767138,"uid":7436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:43:13.000Z","msg":"ACO請一千個<img src=\"/assets/faces/